    <name>ExprCal</name>
    <description>A compact library for compiling and solving complex mathematical expressions (still under tests). To render an expression, Do the following:

String s="1.233---.999.00+sin(2*13+4)/cos(60)tan(45)"; int round_up_scale = 4; double result = new ExpressionRenderer(s, ExpressionRenderer.DEGREE, round_up_scale).render().getResult();</description>
